==<div class="egypt">'''Colonies and Outposts''' 𓎢𓅱𓃭𓅱𓈖𓇋𓅂𓋴 𓄿𓈖𓂧 𓅱𓅲𓏏𓊪𓅱𓋴𓏏𓋴</div>==
Due to '''Level 866''''s hostile environment, deadly traps, common environmental hazards, lack of resources, and '''The Pharaoh''', it is highly difficult to establish any sort of community. All attempts on creating such have resulted in bloody, suffering, and painful deaths.

