</div><div class="egypt">'''Entrances''' 𓅂𓈖𓏏𓂋𓄿𓈖𓎢𓅂𓋴</div>

* Accessing/no-clipping through pyramid-like objects in [[Level 999]].
* Drowning in sand on any [https://backrooms.fandom.com/wiki/Category:Desert desert level].
* Entering ancient areas in [[Level 92]].
* Reading Egyptian quotes out loud in [[Level 46]]. The quotes are located in destroyed stone walls.
* Reading history books in [[Level 80]] has a 30% chance of leading here.

 <div class="egypt">'''Exits''' 𓅂𓇨𓇋𓏏𓋴</div>

*'''Level 866''' may be left by going into the deepest areas of '''The Tomb''' (Aproximatelly 1754,4 meters/5755,90551 feet underground.).
*Noclipping through strange, polished stone formations and structures may lead to [[Ad Memento]] or [[Level 999]].
*Playing with ancient toys may lead to [[Level 859]].
*No-clip through the great wall, and encounter [[Level 833|'''''<u>salvation</u>''''']].
